<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>all right guy • right guy</xh5><p> <i>all right guy</i>—(coll.) a reliable or trustworthy person: We took a big chance by inviting you and ... you turned out to be an <u>all right guy</u>.</p><p><i>right guy—</i>1. <i>= all right guy: </i>I told Gains what the hotel clerk said and how lucky we were he happened to be a <u>right guy</u>. 2. <i>(coll., also: Mr. Right)</i> a perfect romantic or marriage partner: When she moved to Madrid she joked that she would never return home if she met the <u>right guy</u>.</p> </entry>
